name: Duskfall's Manga Aesthetic
description:
Duskfall's Manga Aesthetic

If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

This Model IS GREAT AT:

  • PORTRAITS

  • EATING YOUR LUNCH BEHIND YOUR BACK

  • SMACKING YOU IN THE FACE AT MIDNIGHT

  • Neko, because FFXIV. Don't ask. You were warned.

Problems this model when you don't use certain samplers:

  • Wild proportions

  • BARELY PAYS ATTENTION TO CLOTHING

  • Can't even do a bikini

  • Can't decide on a style, so it's a wild nightmare fuel of every manga from 1950 until now.

  • Bites people for looking at it.

  • Demands you pay it not me.

  • Might need psychological therapy

THERE ARE 3 versions to this and soon coming a merge of all 3.
They all work best at your discretion, and faces etc work a lot better now - but it could be dynamic prompt, it could be we just .. the AI hated us last night?

Data it was trained on all three times:

  • Extremely retro manga (first run)

  • Hands, faces, in all sorts of matter in the second run

  • BOTH sets of data with out the transparent hand PNGs, added in extra realism to keep the faces from borking. Turned out this wasn't needed.

  • SOME Backgrounds, will still train a background model at some stage.

modelVersions.name: 1.5 Final
modelVersions.description: This one was an 8 hour one with a few realistic faces thrown in, some backgrounds.
